title: After Installing Tensorflow when I TRy to verify I getting Follwing error can some body help on this
body_html:

    Required-by:

    3.6.7

  • Bazel version (if compiling from source):
    No compilation used

  • GCC/Compiler version (if compiling from source):
    No compilation used

  • CUDA/cuDNN version:
    No CUDA

  • GPU model and memory:
    No GPU
